    "This dataset is very useful for identifying complex and multi-channel fraud schemes since it contains a wide range of variables, including transaction timing, location, merchant information, and client demographics.",
    "One noteworthy advantage is that it incorporates the most recent fraud patterns, which are essential for creating models that work in the current fraud environments.",
    "However, because of the dataset's imbalance, accurate model training is complex, and the dataset's size and complexity call for thorough preprocessing and feature engineering [88].",
